#: ../../../index.rst:2
msgid "urllib3"
msgstr "urllib3"

#: ../../../index.rst:18
msgid ""
"urllib3 is a powerful, *user-friendly* HTTP client for Python. :ref:`Much of "
"the Python ecosystem already uses <who-uses>` urllib3 and you should too."
msgstr ""
"urllib3 是一個功能強大且\\ *易於使用*\\ 的 Python HTTP 客戶端。:ref:`許多 "
"Python 生態系統已經在使用 <who-uses>` urllib3，您也應該使用它。"

#: ../../../index.rst:21
msgid ""
"urllib3 brings many critical features that are missing from the Python "
"standard libraries:"
msgstr "urllib3 提供了許多 Python 標準程式庫所缺乏的重要功能："

#: ../../../index.rst:24
msgid "Thread safety."
msgstr "執行緒安全。"

#: ../../../index.rst:25
msgid "Connection pooling."
msgstr "連接池。"

#: ../../../index.rst:26
msgid "Client-side TLS/SSL verification."
msgstr "客戶端 TLS/SSL 驗證。"

#: ../../../index.rst:27
msgid "File uploads with multipart encoding."
msgstr "使用 multipart 編碼上傳檔案。"

#: ../../../index.rst:28
msgid "Helpers for retrying requests and dealing with HTTP redirects."
msgstr "用於重試請求及處理 HTTP 重新導向的輔助工具。"

#: ../../../index.rst:29
msgid "Support for gzip, deflate, brotli, and zstd encoding."
msgstr "支援 gzip、deflate、brotli 及 zstd 編碼。"

#: ../../../index.rst:30
msgid "Proxy support for HTTP and SOCKS."
msgstr "支援 HTTP 與 SOCKS 代理。"

#: ../../../index.rst:31
msgid "100% test coverage."
msgstr "100% 測試覆蓋率。"

#: ../../../index.rst:33
msgid "urllib3 is powerful and easy to use:"
msgstr "urllib3 功能強大且易於使用："

#: ../../../index.rst:35
msgid ""
">>> import urllib3\n"
">>> resp = urllib3.request(\"GET\", \"https://httpbin.org/robots.txt\")\n"
">>> resp.status\n"
"200\n"
">>> resp.data\n"
"b\"User-agent: *\\nDisallow: /deny\\n\""
msgstr ""
">>> import urllib3\n"
">>> resp = urllib3.request(\"GET\", \"https://httpbin.org/robots.txt\")\n"
">>> resp.status\n"
"200\n"
">>> resp.data\n"
"b\"User-agent: *\\nDisallow: /deny\\n\""

#: ../../../index.rst:54
msgid "|tideliftlogo|_"
msgstr "|tideliftlogo|_"

#: ../../../index.rst:47
msgid "Tidelift"
msgstr "Tidelift"

#: ../../../index.rst:55
msgid ""
"Professional support for urllib3 is available as part of the `Tidelift "
"Subscription`_.  Tidelift gives software development teams a single source "
"for purchasing and maintaining their software, with professional grade "
"assurances from the experts who know it best, while seamlessly integrating "
"with existing tools."
msgstr ""
"urllib3 的專業支援已包含在 `Tidelift 訂閱服務`_\\ 中。Tidelift 為軟體開發團隊"
"提供單一的採購與維護管道，由最了解軟體的專家提供專業級保障，並能與現有工具無"
"縫整合。"

#: ../../../index.rst:64
msgid "|learn-more|_ |request-a-demo|_"
msgstr "|learn-more|_ |request-a-demo|_"

#: ../../../index.rst:66
msgid "Learn more about Tidelift Subscription"
msgstr "了解更多關於 Tidelift 訂閱服務的資訊"

#: ../../../index.rst:71
msgid "Request a Demo for the Tidelift Subscription"
msgstr "請求 Tidelift 訂閱服務的示範"

#: ../../../index.rst:77
msgid "Installing"
msgstr "安裝方式"

#: ../../../index.rst:79
msgid "urllib3 can be installed with `pip <https://pip.pypa.io>`_"
msgstr "urllib3 可以透過 `pip <https://pip.pypa.io>`_ 進行安裝"

#: ../../../index.rst:81
msgid "$ python -m pip install urllib3"
msgstr "$ python -m pip install urllib3"

#: ../../../index.rst:85
msgid ""
"Alternatively, you can grab the latest source code from `GitHub <https://"
"github.com/urllib3/urllib3>`_:"
msgstr ""
"或者，你也可以從 `GitHub <https://github.com/urllib3/urllib3>`_ 取得最新的來"
"源碼："

#: ../../../index.rst:87
msgid ""
"$ git clone https://github.com/urllib3/urllib3.git\n"
"$ cd urllib3\n"
"$ pip install ."
msgstr ""
"$ git clone https://github.com/urllib3/urllib3.git\n"
"$ cd urllib3\n"
"$ pip install ."

#: ../../../index.rst:94
msgid "Usage"
msgstr "使用方式"

#: ../../../index.rst:96
msgid ""
"The :doc:`user-guide` is the place to go to learn how to use the library and "
"accomplish common tasks. The more in-depth :doc:`advanced-usage` guide is "
"the place to go for lower-level tweaking."
msgstr ""
":doc:`user-guide`\\ 是學習如何使用此程式庫以及完成常見任務的地方。更深入的"
"\\ :doc:`advanced-usage`\\ 指南則適合需要進行底層調整的使用者。"

#: ../../../index.rst:99
msgid ""
"The :doc:`reference/index` documentation provides API-level documentation."
msgstr ":doc:`reference/index`\\ 文件提供了 API 層級的文件。"

#: ../../../index.rst:104
msgid "Who uses urllib3?"
msgstr "誰在使用 urllib3？"

#: ../../../index.rst:106
msgid ""
"`urllib3 is one of the most downloaded packages on PyPI <https://pypistats."
"org/top>`_ and is a dependency of many popular Python packages like "
"`Requests <https://requests.readthedocs.io>`_, `Pip <https://pip.pypa.io>`_, "
"and more!"
msgstr ""
"`urllib3 是 PyPI 上下載量最高的軟體包之一 <https://pypistats.org/top>`_，也是"
"許多熱門 Python 軟體包（如 `Requests <https://requests.readthedocs.io>`_、"
"`Pip <https://pip.pypa.io>`_ 等）的依賴項目！"

